## 13. Emergency/SOS Feature

When you trigger the SOS feature:
- Your **current location** is shared with emergency contacts you've provided (email and/or SMS)
- Your location is shared with our support team (for follow-up)
- Location data is retained for **30 days** performance period
- We may share your location with **local authorities** if required for rescue operations

You can test the SOS feature without sending alerts in the App settings.

