## 15. Regulatory Compliance

### 15.1 Nepal Data Law
We store user data in AWS ap-south-1 (Mumbai) to comply with Nepal's data residency requirements. Data is not transferred to non-compliant regions.

### 15.2 GDPR (For EU travelers)
If you are in the European Union, you have additional rights under the GDPR, including:
- Right to data portability
- Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")
- Right to restrict processing

To exercise these rights, contact privacy@nepaluntrodden.com.

### 15.3 California Privacy Rights (CCPA)
California residents may request information about our data sharing practices by emailing privacy@nepaluntrodden.com.

